item.title: I have a theory
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

[quote=“Primadude, post:4, topic:352955”][quote author=abatssk8ter link=topic=449271.msg3296124#msg3296124 date=1280954790]

I believe that the forum and database was taken down before Jagex took over the domain. I’m not completely sure, though.
[/quote] Idk, man. Jagex sort of popped out of nowhere i don’t think they had time to delete it all.

The owner of the site was obviously sent an email or message before the domain was taken over - this happens with all law-conflicts that involve Jagex and other parties who Jagex have claimed Copyright over.[/quote]No matter what, a Database injection is not hard to execute.
